DENGUE/DHF UPDATE 2007 (05)
***************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
ProMED-mail, a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
[This is not a comprehensive collection of all dengue reports in the
world since the last update. To make updates more complete,
ProMED-mail asks readers to send reports of dengue outbreaks that
they find to <promed@promedmail.org>.]
[1] Paraguay
[2] Bolivia (Santa Cruz): alert
[3] Bolivia (Beni)
